        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> There is a debate in my guild about the use of necros in a CH chain to lenghten it via mind wrack and Zefveers.</P><P>Our mages are throwing a shit attack at the thought of being modrod2 whores.</P><P>My guild has 2 active necros with mindwrack and zefveers and a 3rd thats 58 with mindwrack.</P><P>I have brought up making a cleric group of 4 clerics, a necro and a shamman using mod rod2 + torpor, zefveers and mindwrack.</P><P>We are i guess what you could call a tier2 guild and we are getting ready for an attempt at the AoW, and want to have our mana regen be as high as possible to keep the chain going. We can do an unslowed dual weilding statchoo, in fact that is the closest thing we could find for AoW practice hehe.</P><P>We also have the wizards... they are whining that we need to twich them the whole fight lol but i think i got them taken care of hehe. Does anyone else twich wizards??</P><P>I know alot of you guys like Zaar and Brownivy have thoughts on twiching, i would love to hear them, im not looking for l33t tactics on how to kill mobs we can figure that out, im just wanting info on how effective you guys have found the modrod2/zefveers/MW combo, or what you have found that works better</P><P>Thanks</P><P>Mechalekahi McStinkels<BR>Warlock<BR>Forged Souls<BR>7th Hammer</P><P> </font></td>

