        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> have you guys tried NToV? Whats the hp on your MT?  How many clerics are you using?  How good is your agro control?  How many MT do you have?  How much mana does your clerics have?</P><P>In my experiances on AoW its a 15 min fight he has a 1250 dps and is ruthless when you have mistakes.  This must be the most perfect fight you have ever had or you die.  </P><P>Even Tunare allows some mistakes and allows you to live. I would recomend fighting her first. True its a tad different fight but in my opnion she is easier.  She was good practise for us to kill him.  </P><P>If you have any questions you can pm me or send me a tell in game I play on CT server.  IMO compared to us you guys seem to be asking for a small CR =/ but who knows its hard to gauge 1 guild to another to be honest. I just know what and hw many we had when we lost and how many when we won.  </P><P>BTW mind wrack dont work against him.  theft of vitea does and helps with the heals problem is easier for shaman to torpor =/.  Your mages will just have to suck it up and mod rod and make plenty of them going to need them.  I cant remember how well spells worked I played cleric lasst time since we were low on them.   Next fight i will use necro and try again :).</P><P>Sage Brendayan Warlock<BR>Cohort Chalybeius</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Brendayan on 04/24/2002  11:45:01<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
